{
  "stem": "16106.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he gave me an-- an guard, somebody to accompany me to a place where they collect people who have no homes, so because I am a [GERMAN] from Germany.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he went down the steps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have mentioned that before that, they took me to the bathroom and looked into all my orifices and what have you, couldn't find anything, and kept on saying, don't look-- and that woman who did it says to me, don't look anybody in the eye, don't look them in the eye.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All right, what-- OK, so we walk down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He's about to open the door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, one minute, please.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I scampered up those steps, went back to the office, and yelled, not auf Wiedersehen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't want to see you again any more in my life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that guy got blue in his face-- blue, I tell you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "His eyes were bulging.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He kept on knocking the table and said, once more, I see your chutzpah face, your [GERMAN], that will be the end of you.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I hopped down the steps, I thought I was such a big hero.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that guard took me, and hit me, and hit me, and hit me, and I [INAUDIBLE] He said, you stupid goat, you stupid cow, aren't you lucky you got out, away from those [? 'brothers,' ?] quote unquote?",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You don't know what we went through, watching you at this interrogation, how be worried.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you have the gall to go back up there?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm not talking to you again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[GERMAN]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he marched me to his school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He never even said goodbye to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] unforgivable.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
